Laure Duthilleul https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laure_Duthilleul 0 Laure Duthilleul (born 14 January 1959) is a French actress, director and screenwriter. She has appeared in more than 70 films and television shows since 1981. She has appeared in five films that have been screened at the Cannes Film Festival.
